drop table #Temp
select SampleNo,HISTestCode into #Temp
from TestRequestDetails
group bY SampleNo,HISTestCode 
Having Count(1) > 1

select * from #Temp


while((select COUNT(*) from #Temp) > 0)
begin
	declare @SampleNo varchar(25)
	declare @HISTestCode varchar(25)
	declare @Id bigint
	select top 1 @SampleNo=SampleNo,@HISTestCode=HISTestCode from #Temp
	
	select top 1 @Id = Id from TestRequestDetails where SampleNo = @SampleNo and HISTestCode=@HISTestCode order by id desc
	
	delete from TestParameters where TestRequestDetailsId in 
	(select id from TestRequestDetails where id = @Id)

	delete from TestRequestDetails where id = @Id
	
	delete from #Temp where SampleNo = @SampleNo and HISTestCode=@HISTestCode
end
